{"haf17078bgca04g4639gb947gdd7d5b24268e": ["You're always a pleasure to watch.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "258cc8c0-8445-176e-f0b8-7a520d559517"], "h5749431cg89deg4741g9c16g2bbeb2ddb318": ["Every day, you become stronger. Every night, you grow.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "dfe57e38-da5b-8cc9-c2f6-721432a371d2"], "hd3c12c8cg1e16g4934gb045g833cf687b669": ["But you deserve even more.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "f13d1034-1393-8054-e273-cd29666ee0d5"], "h01146d6dgabd1g4aa8ga10fgdc7b6996eeee": ["*Her fingers flex against her thigh, coiled with tension. Longing.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "069ccb92-c354-6e4f-7e05-a1dee044760d"], "hdcd70775g5c57g4d55gbcd8g759a1b7e3005": ["*His fingers flex against his thigh, coiled with tension. Longing.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "069ccb92-c354-6e4f-7e05-a1dee044760d"], "h25f935b5g8261g4050g9b69gea6a1c6b5627": ["Let me help you.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "d4840c7e-1ce7-30d7-dacd-9fc9e085e43c"], "h6cf5cf74gbb4cg436fg824dg796f026d5814": ["I'm not doing anything until you tell me who you are.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "57de82fb-b022-ec93-9bfa-cf9be697feec"], "hc4cd3198gb374g4be0g81a1gd22248ca1b5a": ["I'm <i>yours.</i>", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "e1556947-25d9-2ee5-e7cf-d35af298ef85"], "h0b57f796gef46g4b58g929dg1e3cc0783396": ["I'm the key to fulfilling your destiny.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "84f0c3a2-a14e-b819-3d20-5732a3c35d0b"], "ha8e4344dgd7bdg45d8g954ag762d89f8dab8": ["Destiny's a big word. Care to narrow it down?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "b5f62368-a120-e6e8-ad32-045c4095268e"], "h94585ba8g6465g44fdg8283gb231ffedcdb7": ["The realms will tremble with the change you bring.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "9184c2b1-944d-cd6e-635d-cf93aceb8823"], "hda32d7e1g90efg4ac7g8b8eg62f369fd6de4": ["A glorious, beautiful renewal.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "db6c4b9c-079b-95bf-7870-bb741fe2849a"], "h817272acg9cd7g49ccga3b7g7ee653f82a4f": ["Help me. This parasite is eating me alive.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "83f88646-9afe-b38e-76ae-71e7027e04e0"], "he472ef36g272dg4a53g923fgda7fc1c96d08": ["I knew you were the right choice. ", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "6b37781c-47b4-67e2-67eb-498bee8cc692"], "h4d39961age644g4ee8g9299g2a8c7c74b63d": ["Let me show you what's to come.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "c3e785ed-8c01-6174-4ac0-00f106ed15d2"], "h34fc15b9g6b87g4480g870ag5e93fe00c5fd": ["Your enemies will fall. The world will bow.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "a935c1ff-8dc0-f242-ee71-5a2d42e98d5b"], "he29fcdd3gb0bdg450fgaa99g5f74c03ccef1": ["You'll have everything you could ever desire.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "df2f69da-feff-1792-76cb-08f86cdcbe73"], "h47120c72gf60dg4582gac49g4d87b9dd3d2e": ["Just let me in.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "681e35ce-2e7c-92bc-5b2a-f3814f81752e"], "ha2b8bdadg3405g41a6ga519g72926e3eabf2": ["Get out of my head. <i>Now.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "b1f2de39-7b18-9a82-431f-72f80b906036"], "h71f22608g4776g465cg8f0ag8fe7353392f2": ["Such an iron will. But you'll be ready soon enough.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "32154fbd-4025-8c2d-63dc-558735280d19"], "h2adb5428g283fg4836ga323g990a9b1f9aae": ["I'll give you a taste of what's to come.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy2_AvD_ROM.html", "7f9f9421-0a37-22f8-7b91-542cb5fda894"]}